{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "dfd2fc4e-8f0a-4241-b4a3-c6626b6f2acf", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/dfd2fc4e-8f0a-4241-b4a3-c6626b6f2acf@2.pkg/1772602101660/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602102141", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/dfd2fc4e-8f0a-4241-b4a3-c6626b6f2acf@2.pkg/1772602101660/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602102141"}, "identifier": "dfd2fc4e-8f0a-4241-b4a3-c6626b6f2acf", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B.有误，甲诗首联诗人回顾平生，但限于篇幅，在写法上是举出入仕和兵败一首一尾两件事来概括，而不是&ldquo;将自己辛苦带兵打仗和朝廷兵败两件事相对举&rdquo;。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>阅读下面两首词，完成下列题目。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;过零丁洋 &nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 文天祥</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>辛苦遭逢起一经，干戈寥落四周星。山河破碎风飘絮，身世浮沉雨打萍。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>惶恐滩头说惶恐。零丁洋里叹零丁。人生自古谁无死？留取丹心照汗青。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;金陵驿二首（其一）<sup>①</sup></span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;文天祥</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>草合离宫转夕晖，孤云飘泊复何依？山河风景元无异，城郭人民半已非。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>满地芦花和我老，旧家燕子傍谁飞？从今别却江南路，化作啼鹃带血归。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【注释】①这首诗是祥兴元年（1278年）文天祥被俘后。次年被押赴元都燕京（今北京）途经金陵时所作。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>对两首词理解和分析不恰当的一项是（　　）</span></p>\n</div>\n", "label": "", "title": "阅读下面两首词，完成下列题目。                                         过零丁洋                                            文天祥辛苦遭逢起一经，干戈寥落四周星。山河破碎风飘絮，身世浮沉雨打萍。惶恐滩头说惶恐。零丁洋里叹零丁。人生自古谁无死？留取丹心照汗青。                             ", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/dfd2fc4e-8f0a-4241-b4a3-c6626b6f2acf@2.pkg/item.json?v=1748322322552", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>甲诗概述了自己的身世命运，表现了慷慨激昂的爱国热情和视死如归的高风亮节，以及舍生取义的人生观，是中华民族传统美德的最高表现。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>甲诗首联诗人回顾平生，但限于篇幅，仅将自己辛苦带兵打仗和朝廷兵败两件事相对举。</span>​</p>\n</div>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p><span>乙诗第一句中的“转”字用得精妙到位，先是用夕阳渐渐西斜、渐渐下落之“动”反衬诗人久久凝望、久久沉思之“静”，突出诗人的无限怅惘。</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>​</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p><span>两首诗的尾联都表现了诗人以死报国的决心。甲诗胸怀坦荡、光明磊落，充满阳刚之气；乙诗凄清哀婉，外柔内刚，沉挚悲壮。</span></p>\n"}], "prompt": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>阅读下面两首词，完成下列题目。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;过零丁洋 &nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 文天祥</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>辛苦遭逢起一经，干戈寥落四周星。山河破碎风飘絮，身世浮沉雨打萍。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>惶恐滩头说惶恐。零丁洋里叹零丁。人生自古谁无死？留取丹心照汗青。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;金陵驿二首（其一）<sup>①</sup></span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;文天祥</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>草合离宫转夕晖，孤云飘泊复何依？山河风景元无异，城郭人民半已非。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>满地芦花和我老，旧家燕子傍谁飞？从今别却江南路，化作啼鹃带血归。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【注释】①这首诗是祥兴元年（1278年）文天祥被俘后。次年被押赴元都燕京（今北京）途经金陵时所作。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>对两首词理解和分析不恰当的一项是（　　）</span></p>\n</div>\n", "object": {"data": ""